<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #3498db;
    }
    p {
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .verification-code {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .company-info {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Dear <%= user.name %>,</h1>
    <p>Thank you for registering with our platform. We are thrilled to have you on board!</p>
    <p>Your registration is almost complete. Please use the following verification code to activate your account:</p>
    <div class="verification-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
    <p>If you did not register for our platform, please disregard this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you again for choosing us!</p>
    <p class="company-info">Best regards,<br>Your Company Name</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
